### V1 결제 요청
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### V1 결제 상태 확인 (verify)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments/verify?orderId=1
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!

### V2 결제 요청
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v2/payments
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### V2 결제 상태 확인 (verify)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v2/payments/verify?orderId=1
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Password1!

