### PG Simulator - 결제 요청
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/payments
X-USER-ID: 135135
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "1351039135",
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451",
  "amount": "5000",
  "callbackUrl": "http://localhost:8080/api/v2/payments/callback"
}

### PG Simulator - 결제 정보 확인
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/payments/20250816:TR:9577c5
X-USER-ID: 135135

### PG Simulator - 주문에 엮인 결제 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/payments?orderId=1351039135
X-USER-ID: 135135
